import React from 'react'; import './About.css'; const About = () => { const teamMembers = [ { name: 'Dr. Sarah Johnson', role: 'Founder & CEO', bio: 'With over 20 years of experience in education and corporate training, Dr. Johnson leads NPY Skills Academy with a vision to transform learning experiences.', image: '/images/team1.jpg' }, { name: 'Michael Chen', role: 'Director of Programs', bio: 'Michael brings expertise in experiential learning and has designed programs that have impacted over 10,000 professionals across various industries.', image: '/images/team2.jpg' }, { name: 'Dr. Emily Rodriguez', role: 'Lead Trainer', bio: 'A certified trainer with a Ph.D. in Adult Education, Emily specializes in leadership development and emotional intelligence training.', image: '/images/team3.jpg' } ]; return (

About NPY Skills Academy

Discover our story, mission, and the passionate team behind transformative learning experiences.

Our Mission

At NPY Skills Academy, we believe in empowering individuals and organizations through innovative learning experiences that combine theoretical knowledge with practical application. Founded in 2002, we have been pioneers in experiential education, helping professionals and organizations achieve their full potential.

Our unique methodology integrates outdoor adventures, classroom learning, and real-world projects to create lasting transformation. We have successfully conducted over 500 programs and touched the lives of more than 10,000 individuals across various sectors.

Meet Our Team

{teamMembers.map((member, index) => (

{member.name}

{member.role}

{member.bio}

))}

Our Core Values

Excellence

We strive for the highest standards in everything we do, from program design to delivery.

Innovation

We continuously evolve our methods to incorporate the latest in educational technology and pedagogy.

Impact

Our success is measured by the lasting positive change we create in individuals and organizations.

Integrity

We conduct our business with honesty, transparency, and ethical practices.

); }; export default About;
